                    </view>
                </view>
                <view class="weui-article__section">                                 <view class="weui-article__h3">2.4 支持账本统计</view>
                    <view class="weui-article__p">
                        如果添加的记事薄为账本信息，系统支持按月统计收支情况
                    </view>
                    <view class="weui-article__p">
                        <image class="weui-article__img" src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/stat1.png" data-src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/stat1.png" bindtap="previewImage" mode="aspectFit" style="height: 180px" />
                        <image class="weui-article__img" src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/stat2.png" data-src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/stat2.png" bindtap="previewImage" mode="aspectFit" style="height: 180px" />
                    </view>    
                    <view class="weui-article__h3">2.5 支持账本分享</view>
                    <view class="weui-article__p">
                        任何的记事记账博都对应的一个二维码，让家人朋友通过该小程序“我的“->”扫一扫“功能，即可和家人朋友一起记录这个记事记账薄，通过“我的“->”记事记账簿管理“可查看每个二维码
                    </view>
                    <view class="weui-article__p">
                        <image class="weui-article__img" src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/share1.png" data-src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/share1.png" bindtap="previewImage" mode="aspectFit" style="height: 180px" />
                        <image class="weui-article__img" src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/share2.png" data-src="http://h5.sumslack.com/wx/help/share2.png" bindtap="previewImage" mode="aspectFit" style="height: 180px" />
                    </view>    
                    <view class="weui-article__h3">2.6 支持记事记账簿管理</view>
                    <view class="weui-article__h3">2.7 制定周计划和月计划</view>
                    <view class="weui-article__p">
                        点击日历最右边的第几周数字可进入周计划编排页面，点击左上角“月”图标可进入月计划编排页面
                    </view>
                </view>
